{"tid":1628250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有招可以學柒婆","createTime":"2019-10-06T01:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T01:53:25.000Z","uid":66895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"50c1530aa8aa1ca85e0ba4739d88ab61a085f53a","tid":1628250,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:50:32.000Z","msg":"知唔知前兩日點解無論本地新聞、國際新聞、定連登嘅輿論集中晒討論裝修、放火？<br />\n<br />\n係因為呢兩日<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無同警察大戰分散注意力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n柒婆有招識玩：自己出錯就用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">另一件事蓋過</span></span>，想傳媒<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中焦點</span></span>就減少警民衝突<br />\n<br />\n早幾日個中五學生胸口中槍，就推個緊急法蒙面法分散輿論<br />\n<br />\n前排係伊館見公眾，想傳媒集中焦點，就唔見有警民衝突<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日大家都見到，街頭唔見太多警察，所以輿論集中咗係示威者行動上。<br />\n<br />\n結論：只要今明兩日有另一啲事分散注意力，前兩日發生嘅事好快就會唔記得。所以今日嘅和理非遊行係非常重要，要將輿論集中去制度暴力上。今日係由和理去保護勇武，係一次大型文宣"},{"pid":"4834fc1ced616cb2ca18021767c52221fa135aa6","tid":1628250,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:51:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19ffec6763a49ad697a706eeb1230c0b3230d799","tid":1628250,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:51:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2096e9af630f4953d2fe06d6bd57c83b8230cd59","tid":1628250,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:52:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac152f6d4553993fb8d7b1a3c062ae6eabc7ef95","tid":1628250,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:52:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70f8d3a2d5bee04af666dbffdafd4d5b00b46e80","tid":1628250,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:52:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77658684a11f47179c06602c7cb176b9b701b7de","tid":1628250,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:53:25.000Z","msg":"個個政府高官都識轉移視線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聲東擊西<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}